# Agent skills — keep the release-automation skill out of the wp.org package
# (it is tracked in git for the team, but must never ship). The 2.2.5 deploy
# leaked .claude because BUILD_DIR bypassed .distignore; the default 10up flow
# applies this file, so .claude/ + the skill stay out of the package.
.claude
.claude/skills/wedocs-release/SKILL.md
